            <article>
                <header>
                    <h2>The Choices We Made</h2>
                    <div class="meta">
                        Posted By<strong> Arpit Sharma</strong><span>(32 comments)</span>
                    </div><!--meta-->
                </header>
                <img src="img/post 1.jpg" alt="Post 1">
                <p> In life , sometimes we have to try to follow our heart not our brain . The decisions we make today decide our future . It’s very easy to choose between right and wrong but to choose the better of two goods , or the lesser of two evils these choices decides our lives .

                </p><p>In life , whether we took a right or a wrong decision the important part is we made a choice , may be it would give us a bad experience but a good decision comes from experience and experience comes from bad decisions .
                    
                </p><p>Our life is a result of our choices if we don’t like our life , it’s time to make better choices . No matter how long we have traveled in the wrong direction , we always have the choice to turn around .</p>
                
            </article>
